snippet.title: Moonlighter 2: The Endless Vault - Official Gameplay Trailer | ID@Xbox
snippet.description:
Join Will on a brand new adventure in Moonlighter 2: The Endless Vault. As revealed during the ID@Xbox showcase, the latest Moonlighter 2: The Endless Vault trailer shows gameplay, enemies you'll fight, and various locations you'll explore in this upcoming sequel to 2018's action RPG. 

Moonlighter 2: The Endless Vault will be available on Windows PC, Steam, Xbox Series X/S, and PS5 in 2025.

#IGN #GAMING
